              </span>
              <span class="commitment-text">
                To increase efficiency by working in mutual trust with our service
                provider partners.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="commitment-item">
              <span class="commitment-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-bullseye">
                </i>
              </span>
              <span class="commitment-text">
                To continuously follow technological and sectoral developments and quickly
                transform them into added value.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="commitment-item">
